OL,3,C'I do this because my little boy
OL,4,Cshould be here': Mum's road safety
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FSchoolchildren are being taught about
OL,8,Froad safety with the help of a charity
OL,9,Ffounded by a grieving mother whose son
OL,10,Fwas killed while walking home from
OL,11,Fschool.
OL,13,FBobby Colleran, six, from Huyton, on
OL,14,Fon Merseyside, died when he stepped
OL,15,Finto the road between parked cars on
OL,16,Fhis way home from school with his mum
OL,17,Fand brothers.
OL,19,FFriday 24 October 2025 marks 11 years
OL,20,Fsince Bobby died when he was hit by a
OL,21,Fvan.
