OL,3,C'I do this because my little boy
OL,4,Cshould be here': Mum's road safety
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FHis mum Joanne Colleran says "Bobby
OL,8,Fknew about road safety", but spotted a
OL,9,Ffriend and it was too late for the
OL,10,Fdriver to stop.
OL,12,FFor over a decade, Joanne has been
OL,13,Ftaking her charity 'Bobby Colleran
OL,14,FTrust' into schools but also wants to
OL,15,Fhelp educate their parents.
