OL,3,C'I do this because my little boy
OL,4,Cshould be here': Mum's road safety
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FSt Margaret Mary's Catholic Junior
OL,8,FSchool are piloting a new e-learning
OL,9,Fvideo created by Joanne who says: "I
OL,10,Fjust think it's so important that
OL,11,Fschools are safe with the 20mph zone,
OL,12,Fthe pavement parking, children are
OL,13,Freally small and they should be able
OL,14,Fto go to and from school safely," she
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"He knew about road safety and I think
OL,18,Fthat is what spears me on a lot
OL,19,Fbecause he knew about road safety and
OL,20,Fa child is a child, aren't they."
