OL,3,C'I do this because my little boy
OL,4,Cshould be here': Mum's road safety
OL,5,Ccampaign
OL,7,FJoanne believes that if drivers are
OL,8,Fgoing slower, there's more of a chance
OL,9,Fthat they have enough time to break.
OL,11,F"The parking also had a lot to do with
OL,12,FBobby, with the visibility, because
OL,13,Fwhen the cars are all over the
OL,14,Fpayment, they can't see if a child
OL,15,Fdoes run out."
OL,17,FShe added: "For a child we learn as
OL,18,Fmuch as we can the basics, but just be
OL,19,Fcareful by roads to let them know that
OL,20,Fthere are dangers out there and also
OL,21,Fto help the parents too."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
